overview:
Galaxy Builders is a licensed and insured, residential and commercial remodeling contractor.

With over a combined 50 years of home and business remodeling experience, Galaxy Builders Inc has proudly worked together with many of our residential and commercial clients to create beautiful projects that they can enjoy for years to come. Jacksonville, Florida based Galaxy Builders Inc. is locally owned and operated.
